<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>She showed off her catwalk skills at Milan Digital Fashion Week in Milan, Italy, last month.</p>

<p>And Taylor Hill displayed her model frame as she jetted into Venice on Tuesday ahead of the 77th Film Festival.</p>

<p>The Victoria's Secret Angel, 24, cut a low-key ensemble as she put on a leggy figure in a pair of high-waisted denim shorts.</p>

<p>Landed! Taylor Hill displayed her model frame as she jetted into Venice on Tuesday ahead of the 77th Film Festival</p>

<p>Taylor teamed the item of clothing with a chic white shirt, which she left slightly unbuttoned and tucked into her bottoms.</p>

<p>Adding some stylish touches, the model opted for a black belt, pearl pendant earrings, grey trainers and a purple Gucci handbag.</p>

<p>Taylor styled her brunette locks into a relaxed halfback swept away hairdo, she appeared to go makeup-free.</p>

<p>Stylish: The Victoria's Secret Angel, 24, cut a low-key ensemble as she put on a leggy figure in a pair of high-waisted denim shorts</p>

<p>Finishing touches: Taylor teamed the item of clothing with a chic white shirt, which she left slightly unbuttoned and tucked into her bottoms</p>

<p>Details: Adding some stylish touches, the model opted for a black belt, pearl pendant earrings, grey trainers and a purple Gucci handbag</p>

<p>Taking cautious measures amid the Covid-19 crisis, she wore a protective white face mask for her stroll.</p>

<p>The Venice Film Festival is one of the world's oldest award ceremonies and is listed as one of the 'Big Five' events. It starts on 2 September and ends on the 12 September. </p>

<p>The model has been in Italy for the last few weeks, attending several shows during Milan Digital Fashion Week.   </p>

<p>Cautious: Taking cautious measures amid the Covid-19 crisis, she wore a protective white face mask for her stroll</p>

<p>Exciting! The Venice Film Festival is one of the world's oldest award ceremonies and is listed as one of the 'Big Five' events. It starts on 2 September and ends on the 12 September</p>

<p>Taylor is an Illinois native, who grew up in Colorado, and was discovered by a fashion photographer when she was just 14. </p>

<p>She kickstarted her modelling career by being featured in an Intimissimi's catalogue in 2013, which led to a print campaign in Forever 21.</p>

<p>Since then, she went on to become a popular Victoria's Secret Angel, beginning in 2015, and has appeared in many of the top high-fashion publications and fashion shows around the world.</p>

